item.title: First Post
item.description: Hi there! Welcome to my first post. This is the start of a new adventure in building some stuff and writing about it. Finding Passion For the last little while since I have been out of school and have started working in a “real” job, I have been trying to figure out my place in this world of software. I guess in reflection, I’ve been searching for what I am actually passionate about.
